0032|- [HelpText]
0034|*Getting information from the Web by F1 key combinations
0036|*F1 G      calls Google by the current keyword(s).
0037|*F1 S      calls Google by the current keyword(s) and "Survo".
0038|*F1 W      calls Wikipedia by the current keyword(s).
0039|*F1 D      calls the Free Online Dictionary by the current keyword(s).
0041|*Before pressing the above F1 key combinations the cursor must
0042|*  touch the keyword in the edit field, or
0043|*  touch the space between a combination of two keywords.
0044|*A sequence of several keywords can also be painted by the rightmost
0045|*mouse button.
0047|*The default settings for key codes above can be changed by
0048|*SURVO.APU lines of the following form
0050|*F1-code     SURVO.APU
0051|- shadow W: [LINK(http://www.google.com/search?q=)] [/LINK]
0052|*F1 g        google=http://www.google.com/search?q=
S   |                    WWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWW
0053|- shadow W: [LINK(http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/)] [/LINK]
0054|*F1 W        wiki=http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/
S   |                  WWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWW
0055|- shadow W: [LINK(http://www.thefreedictionary.com/)] [/LINK]
0056|*W1 D        dict=http://www.thefreedictionary.com/
S   |                  WWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWW
0059|*User-defined F1 codes for Web links
0061|*Ten various F1 Web settings can be set by lines
0062|*web0, web1, web2,..., web9 corresponding to codes
0063|*F1 0, F1 1, F1 2,..., F1 9
0065|*For example, activating the command
0067|- shadow W: [LINK(http://www.youtube.com/results?search_query=)] [/LINK]
0068|*SYSTEM web1=http://www.youtube.com/results?search_query=
S   |             WWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWW
0070|*gives access to YouTube pages in the current Survo session.
0071|*Then by touching the word Sibelius in the edit field and by F1 1
0072|*we get hundreds of links to videos where music of Sibelius is played.
0073|*The same YouTube setting will be created permanently by the command
0075|- shadow W: [LINK(http://www.youtube.com/results?search_query=)] [/LINK]
0076|*SYS    web1=http://www.youtube.com/results?search_query=
S   |             WWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWW
0080|*User-defined F1 codes for Web links (continued)
0082|*These settings can be defined even more accurately by giving, for
0083|*example,
0085|- shadow W: [LINK(http://www.google.com/search?q=||survo||+||%22)] [/LINK]
0086|*web7=http://www.google.com/search?q=||survo||+||%22
S   |      WWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWW
0087|*where || works as a delimiter for the following items:
0088|- shadow W: [LINK(http://www.google.fi/search?q=)] [/LINK]
0089|*http://www.google.fi/search?q=    address of the form http://
S   | WWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWW
0090|*survo                             additional keyword
0091|*+                                 separator of keywords
0092|*%22                               "quotation mark"
0094|*"quotation mark" is a string of characters surrounding the sequence
0095|*of keywords. %22 is the inherent notation for it in Google.
0096|*The defaults are: no additional keyword, separator is '+', no
0097|*"quotation mark".
